<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" language="java" %>
<%@ taglib prefix="c" uri="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core" %>

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: April 7, 2026</p>

            <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">We collect information that you provide directly to us, including:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>Name, email address, phone number, and contact information</li>
                        <li>Profile information including photos and preferences</li>
                        <li>PG listing details, photos, and property information</li>
                        <li>Payment and billing information</li>
                        <li>Messages and communications through our platform</li>
                        <li>Reviews and ratings you provide</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">We use the information we collect to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
                        <li>Process transactions and send related information</li>
                        <li>Send you technical notices and support messages</li>
                        <li>Respond to your comments and questions</li>
                        <li>Match tenants with suitable PG accommodations and roommates</li>
                        <li>Detect, prevent, and address fraud and security issues</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Information Sharing</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">We may share your information in the following circumstances:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>With PG owners when you inquire about or book a property</li>
                        <li>With potential roommates when you use our roommate matching service</li>
                        <li>With service providers who perform services on our behalf</li>
                        <li>When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
                    <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>Access and receive a copy of your personal data</li>
                        <li>Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
                        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
                        <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us:</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-envelope text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>Email: support@pgfinder.com</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-phone text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>Phone: +91 98765 43210</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>Address: Bangalore, India</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
                <a href="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i>Back to Home
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
